SHIFT LEFT~

________________________________________

SHIFT LEFT shifts the text in a marked
area one position to the left.
________________________________________

SHIFT LEFT deletes the first character of each line of the marked
area, shifting the remaining characters in and to the right of
the marked area left one column.

In character marked areas, the marks are updated appropriately.

See also SHIFT RIGHT.







SHIFT RIGHT~

________________________________________

SHIFT RIGHT shifts the text in a
marked area one position to the right.
________________________________________

SHIFT RIGHT inserts a blank before the first marked character on
each line of the marked area, shifting the remaining characters
in and to the right of the marked area right one column.

In character marked areas, the marks are updated appropriately.

Shifting a nonblank character past column 255 displays a message
that the line has been truncated.

See also SHIFT LEFT.





